.com/thumb/msid-77689304,width-160,height-120,imgsize-91575/view-states-are-the-biggest-losers-in-gst-sharing-formula.jpg" alt="View: States are the biggest losers in GST sharing formula"></span></a><h3><a href="/small-biz/gst/view-states-are-the-biggest-losers-in-gst-sharing-formula/articleshow/77689304.cms" data-conttype="100">View: States are the biggest losers in GST sharing formula</a></h3><time>22 Aug, 2020, 12:25PM IST</time><p>​​The track record so far of the present government toward states demonstrates a betrayal of trust so crucial not just for India&rsquo;s federal polity, but also for its economic recovery.</p></div><div class="eachStory" id="sid77689388"><a href="/small-biz/gst/gst-registration-after-physical-verification-of-biz-place-if-aadhaar-not-authenticated-cbic/articleshow/77689388.cms"><span class="imgContainer"><img height="120" width="160" class="lazy" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-42031747,width-160,height-120/etlogo.jpg" data-original="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-77689388,width-160,height-120,imgsize-99057/gst-registration-after-physical-verification-of-biz-place-if-aadhaar-not-authenticated-cbic.jpg" alt="GST registration after physical verification of biz place if Aadhaar not authenticated: CBIC"></span></a><h3><a href="/small-biz/gst/gst-registration-after-physical-verification-of-biz-place-if-aadhaar-not-authenticated-cbic/articleshow/77689388.cms">GST registration after physical verification of biz place if Aadhaar not authenticated: CBIC</a></h3><time>22 Aug, 2020, 12:32PM IST</time><p>In a notification, the Central Board of Indirect Taxes and Customs (CBIC) said when an applicant for GST registration opts for authentication of Aadhaar number, he shall, with effect from Friday (August 21), undertake the said authentication while submitting an application. </p></div><div class="eachStory" id="sid77651855"><a href="/small-biz/gst/41st-gst-council-meet-covid-makes-for-grim-backdrop-as-battle-brews-over-revenue-sharing/articl